@KTBMedia
 The original TSRP is a good vanilla hack, but TSRP Reloaded is a really amazing game. It was my favorite SMW hack until TSRP 2 Reloaded came out last year.
MGU is great, it has a lot of good gimmicks and great level design. I've played MGU2 too, and even though I enjoyed it I feel like it didn't hit all the right spots like MGU. Still a great hack though.
